<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:91.34px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Willow vs Freemie Breast Pump Comparison</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:134.30px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Hands-free breast pumps are a blessing for new moms. But, which hands-free breast pump</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:148.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">should you get, Willow or Freemie? In the Willow vs Freemie breast pump comparison, we’ll</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:163.46px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">discuss both products in detail. We’ll tell you how they are different, why you should buy them,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:177.98px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">list their compelling features, pros and cons, and share the experiences of new moms with both</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:192.50px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">products. Our expert moms and dads tested over 50 hands-free breast pumps on the market,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:207.02px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">before narrowing down their choice to Willow and Freemie breast pumps. It was truly a</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:221.54px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">challenge for our experts to pick the </span><A HREF="https://thebabyswag.com/best-breast-pump/">best breast pump</A> </span><span class="cls_002"> out of the two. But, at the end of the</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:236.18px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">research, they had a clear choice in front of them. Can’t wait to know? Read further.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:268.85px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">Willow vs Freemie Breast Pump - Main Differences</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:292.97px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Before moving to the detailed reviews of both Willow and Freemie Breast Pumps, let’s quickly</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:307.49px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">look at their main differences:</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:336.65px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">●   Willow Breast Pump is a hands-free, wireless breast pump, whereas Freemie is a </span><A HREF="https://thebabyswag.com/top-5-best-double-electric-breast-pumps/">double</A> </span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:351.17px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008"> </span><A HREF="https://thebabyswag.com/top-5-best-double-electric-breast-pumps/">electric</A> <span class="cls_002"> hands-free, wired breast pump</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:365.69px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">●   Willow Breast Pump operates on battery, whereas Freemie stays connected to an</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:380.21px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">electric outlet throughout the pumping session</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:394.73px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">●   Willow Breast Pump comes with spill-proof </span><A HREF="https://thebabyswag.com/top-5-milk-storage-bags-breastfeeding/">milk bags</A> </span><span class="cls_002"> or reusable storage containers for</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:409.39px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">collecting milk, whereas Freemie comes with collections cups that cannot be used to</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:423.91px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">store milk</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:438.43px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">●   Unlike the Freemie Breast Pump, Willow comes with a clear, transparent flange that</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:452.95px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">allows you to keep track of how much milk you have collected</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:467.59px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">●   Freemie Breast Pump is more affordable and reasonably priced than Willow</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:500.23px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">Willow vs Freemie Breast Pump - A Detailed Comparison</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:538.87px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">So, we’ve already listed the key differences between Willow and Freemie breast pumps.  Now,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:553.39px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">let’s look at the detailed review of each product and see what our experts have to say.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:584.14px" class="cls_006"><span class="cls_006">Willow Breast Pump</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:620.74px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">With the Willow Breast Pump you can do pretty much everything while you are collecting milk</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:635.38px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">for your baby. You can cook, clean the dishes, go grocery shopping or do yoga. Moreover, you</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:649.90px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">don’t need a hands-free pumping bra. So, what exactly is the Willow Breast Pump?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:678.94px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">The Willow Breast Pump is an innovative hands-free breast pump that allows moms to pump</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:693.58px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">without using their hands. You get two breast pumps; one for each side. You also get 24 milk</span></div>
</div>
