<div style="position:absolute;left:0px;top:0px">
<img src="{{ asset('img/background6.jpg')}}" width=612 height=792></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:71.28px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">collection bags, two flanges, a battery charger, two cleaning brushes, two flex tubes and two</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:85.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">carrying bags. All you need to do is place them inside your bra, position them to latch and</span></div>
