<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:434.95px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">comfortable using the reusable storage container, you’ll have to buy it separately. Nevertheless,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:449.59px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">just like the breast pump, you can purchase the breast pump accessories also with your FSA or</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:464.11px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">HSA.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:492.79px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">Notable features:</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:529.39px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">●   All-in-one breast pump that can easily fit in your bra</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:90.02px;top:544.03px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">●   Allows you to pump hands-free</span></div>
